snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
SW Galactic Connexions ►► http://bit.ly/EnterGoldDiscGiveaway
Pick up Star Wars: Battlefront today at your Local Walmart

A long, long time ago in a galaxy far, far away... Okay not really. More like a few days ago from the comfort of our couch Steph and I dive into the Star Wars spirit in honor of the new Battlefront. Not only do we shoot our way through the dark forces of the Empire; but I also do my very first giveaway with Star Wars Galactic Connexions and a brand new PS4! 

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!
Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: Wii Sports Ugliest Mii Ever! ►► http://bit.ly/1QqXRIA 
HiLite: MatPat Chokes in Megaman ►► http://bit.ly/1S1lFBG
HiLite: Chubby Bunny Singoff  ►► http://bit.ly/1LzAN4D

***Thanks to the support from Walmart and EA for helping us make this all possible.***
snippet.title: Star Wars Battlefront - Darth MatPat's Web of LIES!
